Introduction.
-------------
sqladmin is a Java based free tool for sending queries and editing table contents using any jdbc driver.

This tool allows exporting and importing table rows to and from XML files You can also save and
load SQL text queries for future use.

Feel free to make changes to source code and send any comments.

Requirements.
-------------
You need 
1. Java 2 Runtime Environment (1.2 and avobe) 
	http://java.sun.com

2. jaxp. Java API for XML processing.  Avalaible from Sun Microsystems
	http://java.sun.com/xml/downloads/javaxmlpack.html

3. Java 2 SDK to compile (optional)


Install instructions
----------------------
Read README.linux and README.win32 for plaftorm specific instructions.

